# Security Control & Compliance Audit

## Overview
Simulated internal IT audit assessing cybersecurity controls, governance practices, and regulatory compliance for a retail organization.

## Frameworks
- NIST CSF
- GDPR
- PCI DSS
- SOC Controls

## Scope
- Access Controls
- Asset Management
- Data Protection
- Security Governance
- Disaster Recovery

## Key Findings
- Excessive privileged access
- Missing disaster recovery planning
- Weak password governance
- Lack of IDS monitoring
- Inadequate encryption controls

## Recommendations
- Implement RBAC
- Enforce Least Privilege
- Deploy IDS
- Improve Encryption
- Establish Disaster Recovery Program

## Skills Demonstrated
- IT Audit
- Risk Assessment
- Compliance Analysis
- Security Governance
- Security Controls Review

## Outcome
Identified critical security gaps and provided remediation recommendations aligned with industry standards and regulatory requirements.
